## Risk Mitigation Summary

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|-----------|
| Planning Center/Breeze launch competing feature | Medium | High | Move fast MVP; own "team lead approval workflow" deeply; position as complementary tool. |
| Market too niche (only churches want scheduling) | Low | Medium | Horizontal expansion built into roadmap (schools, nonprofits); test messaging early. |
| ChMS API integration breaks | Low | Medium | Monitor API docs closely; maintain CSV fallback; version-lock dependencies. |
| Beta church churn (mismatch expectations) | Medium | Medium | Weekly feedback loops; prioritize their top 3 pains; iterate fast. |
| Pricing misjudgment | Low | Low | A/B test landing page; adjust tiers based on early feedback; annual discount incentivizes commitment. |
| Solo build burnout (tech debt) | Medium | High | Ship MVP early (no perfection); use no-code/low-code where appropriate (Zapier, Resend templates); set weekly boundaries. |
| SEO not working (no organic traffic) | Low | Low | Start content strategy early (week 2); consistency matters more than virality; build 20+ posts before expecting traffic. |

